description: Final Fantasy VII Rebirth is a monumental title, both in its scope, and its overall incredible gameplay. The narrative and overall writing of the game elevated FFVII's original story on nearly every level. However, after spending nearly 100 hours in Rebirth's Open World, and checking off just about every World Intel item Chadley dished out, Dave Klein came away with plenty of praise, but also a fair bit of criticism in how the open world, specifically, was handled.
title: How Final Fantasy VII Rebirth Got Open Worlds Right (And Wrong)

description:
At PAX East, Lucy got a behind-closed-doors hands off look at Dune: Awakening, the upcoming survival MMO from Funcom. Here are five things she learned. 

The spice sure is flowing right now. We’ve seen the movie, read the book, bought the hideous popcorn bucket, and yet, we’re still eager for more Dune in our lives. Well good news everyone, Funcom is working on an open-world survival MMO called Dune: Awakening. Recently at PAX East, Lucy saw a presentation of the game behind closed doors. From crafting and survival mechanics, to avoiding the giant sandworms that call Arrakis home, here are five things that caught her eye. 

Dune: Awakening is slated to release on PC, Xbox Series X|S, and PlayStation 5, but currently has no set release date.

#gaming #dunewakening #gamespot
title: Dune: Awakening - 5 Things To Know
